Account Deletion Request

To request deletion of your Zagros Express account and all associated data, please contact us at:

Email: zagros3321@gmail.com

What to include in your request:

Your registered phone number
"Account Deletion Request" in the subject line
What happens when you request deletion:

Your account will be permanently deleted
All personal information (name, phone number, addresses) will be removed
Your order history will be deleted
This action cannot be undone
Alternative method:
You can also delete your account directly within the Zagros Express app by going to your Profile settings and selecting "Delete Account."

We will process your deletion request within 7 days and confirm via WhatsApp or email.
